{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# NES-VMC: 使用 NetKet 原生 API 求解扩展系统\n",
    "\n",
    "本 notebook 使用 NetKet 的原生 API（MCState + VMC）来求解扩展系统的基态，\n",
    "然后通过局域能量矩阵对角化得到原系统的激发态能量。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 核心步骤\n",
    "\n",
    "1. 构建 TotalAnsatz（行列式形式的波函数）\n",
    "2. 构建扩展哈密顿量算子\n",
    "3. 使用 MCState + VMC 训练扩展系统\n",
    "4. 采样计算局域能量矩阵\n",
    "5. 对角化得到激发态能量"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 导入必要的库"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import jax\n",
    "import jax.numpy as jnp\n",
    "import netket as nk\n",
    "import netket.experimental as nkx\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from pyscf import gto, scf, fci\n",
    "from flax import nnx\n",
    "import optax\n",
    "from functools import partial\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置 JAX 浮点精度\n",
    "jax.config.update(\"jax_enable_x64\", True)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"NetKet version: {nk.__version__}\")\n",
    "print(f\"JAX version: {jax.__version__}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 设置分子系统（H₂ 分子）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# H₂ 分子定义\n",
    "bond_length = 1.4  # Bohr\n",
    "geometry = [('H', (0., 0., 0.)), ('H', (bond_length, 0., 0.))]\n",
    "mol = gto.M(atom=geometry, basis='STO-3G', verbose=0)\n",
    "mf = scf.RHF(mol).run(verbose=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "# FCI 精确基准\n",
    "cisolver = fci.FCI(mf)\n",
    "cisolver.nroots = 4\n",
    "E_fcis, fcivec = cisolver.kernel()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"=\" * 60)\n",
    "print(\"H₂ FCI 基准能量 (STO-3G)\")\n",
    "print(\"=\" * 60)\n",
    "for i, e in enumerate(E_fcis):\n",
    "    exc_eV = (e - E_fcis[0]) * 27.2114\n",
    "    print(f\"E{i} = {e:.8f} Ha  |  激发能: {exc_eV:.4f} eV\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 定义原始哈密顿量和 Hilbert 空间"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 将 PySCF 分子转为 NetKet 离散算符\n",
    "ha_original = nkx.operator.from_pyscf_molecule(mol)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 原始 Hilbert 空间\n",
    "hi_original = nkx.hilbert.SpinOrbitalFermions(\n",
    "    n_orbitals=2,\n",
    "    s=1/2,\n",
    "    n_fermions_per_spin=(1, 1),\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# NES-VMC 参数\n",
    "K = 2  # 需要计算的态数（基态 + 1 个激发态）\n",
    "n_spin_orbitals = hi_original.size\n",
    "\n",
    "# 扩展 Hilbert 空间：K 个副本的直积\n",
    "hi_extended = hi_original ** K\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"原始 Hilbert 空间大小: {hi_original.size}\")\n",
    "print(f"扩展 Hilbert 空间大小: {hi_extended.size}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 定义 TotalAnsatz（行列式形式的波函数）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "class SingleStateAnsatz(nnx.Module):\n",
    "    \"\"\"单态 Ansatz\"\"\"\n",
    "    def __init__(self, n_spin_orbitals: int, hidden_dim: int = 16, *, rngs: nnx.Rngs):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.linear1 = nnx.Linear(n_spin_orbitals, hidden_dim, rngs=rngs, param_dtype=complex)\n",
    "        self.linear2 = nnx.Linear(hidden_dim, hidden_dim, rngs=rngs, param_dtype=complex)\n",
    "        self.output = nnx.Linear(hidden_dim, 1, rngs=rngs, param_dtype=complex)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __call__(self, x):\n",
    "        h = nnx.tanh(self.linear1(x.astype(complex)))\n",
    "        h = nnx.tanh(self.linear2(h))\n",
    "        out = self.output(h)\n",
    "        return jnp.squeeze(out)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "class TotalAnsatz(nnx.Module):\n",
    "    \"\"\"NES 总 Ansatz: 输入 K 个副本状态，返回 det[ψ_j(x^i)]\"\"\"\n",
    "    def __init__(self, n_spin_orbitals: int, n_states: int = K, hidden_dim: int = 16):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.n_states = n_states\n",
    "        self.n_spin_orbitals = n_spin_orbitals\n",
    "\n",
    "        key = jax.random.key(42)\n",
    "        keys = jax.random.split(key, n_states)\n",
    "\n",
    "        self.single_ansatz_list = [\n",
    "            SingleStateAnsatz(\n",
    "                n_spin_orbitals,\n",
    "                hidden_dim,\n",
    "                rngs=nnx.Rngs(keys[i])\n",
    "            )\n",
    "            for i in range(n_states)\n",
    "        ]\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __call__(self, x_batch):\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        x_batch: (n_states, n_spin_orbitals) -> (psi_total, M)\n",
    "        M_{ij} = ψ_j(x^i)\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        K_state = self.n_states\n",
    "        M = []\n",
    "        for i in range(K_state):\n",
    "            row = [self.single_ansatz_list[j](x_batch[i]) for j in range(K_state)]\n",
    "            M.append(jnp.array(row))\n",
    "        M = jnp.stack(M)\n",
    "        psi_total = jnp.linalg.det(M)\n",
    "        return psi_total, M"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. 构建扩展哈密顿量算子\n",
    "\n",
    "由于 NetKet 的自定义算子限制，我们使用一种替代方法：\n",
    "直接使用原始哈密顿量，但在计算期望值时考虑扩展系统的结构。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 由于扩展哈密顿量算子的实现比较复杂，我们使用另一种方法：\n",
    "# 使用原始哈密顿量，但修改损失函数来计算扩展系统的能量\n",
    "\n",
    "# 转换为 JAX 兼容的算子\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    ha_original_jax = ha_original.to_jax_operator()\n",
    "    print(\"✓ 成功转换为 JAX 兼容算子\")\n",
    "except Exception as e:\n",
    "    print(f\"✗ 无法转换为 JAX 算子: {e}\")\n",
    "    ha_original_jax = ha_original"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. 创建采样器"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 创建采样器\n",
    "sampler = nk.sampler.MetropolisLocal(\n",
    "    hi_extended,\n",
    "    n_chains=16,\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"采样器: {sampler}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. 定义局部能量计算函数（用于自定义损失）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def compute_H_psi_for_single_state(ha, single_ansatz, x):\n",
    "    \"\"\"计算单个态的 H|ψ>\"\"\"\n",
    "    x_conn, mels = ha.get_conn_padded(x)\n",
    "    psi_conn = jax.vmap(single_ansatz)(x_conn)\n",
    "    return jnp.sum(mels * psi_conn)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def compute_H_Psi_matrix(ha, total_ansatz, x_batch):\n",
    "    \"\"\"计算 HΨ 矩阵\"\"\"\n",
    "    K = total_ansatz.n_states\n",
    "    H_mat = []\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for i in range(K):\n",
    "        row = []\n",
    "        for j in range(K):\n",
    "            v = compute_H_psi_for_single_state(ha, total_ansatz.single_ansatz_list[j], x_batch[i])\n",
    "            row.append(v)\n",
    "        H_mat.append(row)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return jnp.array(H_mat, dtype=complex)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def compute_local_energy_matrix(ha, total_ansatz, x_batch, eps=1e-6):\n",
    "    \"\"\"计算局部能量矩阵\"\"\"\n",
    "    psi, M = total_ansatz(x_batch)\n",
    "    M_reg = M + eps * jnp.eye(M.shape[0], dtype=M.dtype)\n",
    "    H_Psi = compute_H_Psi_matrix(ha, total_ansatz, x_batch)\n",
    "    E_matrix = jnp.linalg.solve(M_reg, H_Psi)\n",
    "    E_loc = jnp.trace(E_matrix)\n",
    "    return E_loc, E_matrix"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 8. 使用 NetKet 原生 API 训练\n",
    "\n",
    "由于 TotalAnsatz 的输出是复数（行列式），我们需要自定义期望值计算。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 实例化 TotalAnsatz\n",
    "total_ansatz = TotalAnsatz(\n",
    "    n_spin_orbitals=n_spin_orbitals,\n",
    "    n_states=K,\n",
    "    hidden_dim=16,\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"✓ 创建 TotalAnsatz\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 定义 forward 函数（供 MCState 使用）\n",
    "def forward_fn(params, x):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    params: TotalAnsatz 的参数\n",
    "    x: 扩展系统的组态，形状 (K * n_spin_orbitals,)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    返回: log|Ψ|\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 重塑为 (K, n_spin_orbitals)\n",
    "    x_reshaped = x.reshape(K, n_spin_orbitals)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算波函数值\n",
    "    # 注意：这里需要将 params 应用到模型上\n",
    "    # 由于 NNX 的限制，我们需要使用 nnx.merge\n",
    "    graph_def, variables = params\n",
    "    model = nnx.merge(graph_def, variables)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    psi, _ = model(x_reshaped)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return jnp.log(jnp.abs(psi) + 1e-12)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 由于 NetKet 的 MCState 需要特定的模型接口，我们使用自定义训练循环\n",
    "# 但参考 NetKet 的标准流程\n",
    "\n",
    "# 分离模型参数\n",
    "graph_def, params = nnx.split(total_ansatz)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 初始化采样器状态\n",
    "sampler_state = sampler.init_state(lambda p, x: forward_fn(p, x), (graph_def, params), seed=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"✓ 初始化采样器状态\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 9. 训练循环（参考 NetKet 标准流程）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 定义损失函数和梯度\n",
    "def loss_fn(params, ha, x_batch):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    损失函数：局部能量矩阵的迹\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数:\n",
    "        params: 模型参数 (graph_def, variables)\n",
    "        ha: 原始哈密顿量\n",
    "        x_batch: (n_samples, K, n_spin_orbitals) 的样本\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    graph_def, variables = params\n",
    "    model = nnx.merge(graph_def, variables)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 批量计算局部能量\n",
    "    def single_loss(x):\n",
    "        E_loc, _ = compute_local_energy_matrix(ha, model, x)\n",
    "        return E_loc.real\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 对所有样本计算平均\n",
    "    E_locs = jax.vmap(single_loss)(x_batch)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return E_locs.mean()\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "value_and_grad = jax.value_and_grad(loss_fn, argnums=0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 优化器\n",
    "optimizer = optax.chain(\n",
    "    optax.clip_by_global_norm(1.0),\n",
    "    optax.adam(learning_rate=0.01)\n",
    ")\n",
    "opt_state = optimizer.init(params)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 训练参数\n",
    "n_iter = 300\n",
    "chain_length = 200\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 60)\n",
    "print(\"开始训练扩展系统（参考 NetKet 标准流程）...\")\n",
    "print(\"=\" * 60)\n",
    "\n",
    "from tqdm import tqdm\n",
    "\n",
    "for step in tqdm(range(n_iter)):\n",
    "    # 重置采样器并采样\n",
    "    sampler_state = sampler.reset(lambda p, x: forward_fn(p, x), (graph_def, params), sampler_state)\n",
    "    samples, sampler_state = sampler.sample(\n",
    "        lambda p, x: forward_fn(p, x), (graph_def, params), state=sampler_state, chain_length=chain_length\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 重塑样本\n",
    "    samples_flat = samples.reshape(-1, K, n_spin_orbitals)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 计算损失和梯度\n",
    "    loss_val, grads = value_and_grad(\n",
    "        (graph_def, params), ha_original_jax, samples_flat\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 更新参数\n",
    "    grad_graph, grad_vars = grads\n",
    "    updates, opt_state = optimizer.update(grad_vars, opt_state, params)\n",
    "    params = optax.apply_updates(params, updates)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 打印日志\n",
    "    if step % 50 == 0:\n",
    "        print(f\"Step {step:4d} | Loss = {loss_val:.6f} Ha\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 合并最终模型\n",
    "total_ansatz = nnx.merge(graph_def, params)\n",
    "print(\"\\n✓ 训练完成\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 10. 采样计算局域能量矩阵"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 最终采样\n",
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 60)\n",
    "print(\"最终采样，计算局域能量矩阵...\")\n",
    "print(\"=\" * 60)\n",
    "\n",
    "final_samples, _ = sampler.sample(\n",
    "    lambda p, x: forward_fn(p, x), (graph_def, params), state=sampler_state, chain_length=1000\n",
    ")\n",
    "final_samples_flat = final_samples.reshape(-1, K, n_spin_orbitals)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"样本数: {final_samples_flat.shape[0]}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 计算平均局域能量矩阵\n",
    "def compute_average_energy_matrix(total_ansatz, samples, ha):\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    计算平均局域能量矩阵\n",
    "    \n",
    "    参数:\n",
    "        total_ansatz: TotalAnsatz 模型\n",
    "        samples: (n_samples, K, n_spin_orbitals) 的样本\n",
    "        ha: 原始哈密顿量\n",
    "    \n",
    "    返回:\n",
    "        E_avg: 平均局部能量\n",
    "        E_matrix_avg: 平均局域能量矩阵\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    def single_E_matrix(x):\n",
    "        _, E_matrix = compute_local_energy_matrix(ha, total_ansatz, x)\n",
    "        return E_matrix\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 批量计算\n",
    "    E_matrices = jax.vmap(single_E_matrix)(samples)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 平均\n",
    "    E_matrix_avg = E_matrices.mean(axis=0)\n",
    "    E_avg = jnp.trace(E_matrix_avg)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return E_avg, E_matrix_avg\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "# 计算平均局域能量矩阵\n",
    "E_avg, E_matrix_avg = compute_average_energy_matrix(\n",
    "    total_ansatz, final_samples_flat, ha_original_jax\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\n平均局部能量: {E_avg:.6f} Ha\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\n平均局域能量矩阵:\")\n",
    "print(E_matrix_avg)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 11. 对角化得到激发态能量"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 对称化矩阵\n",
    "E_matrix_sym = (E_matrix_avg + E_matrix_avg.conj().T) / 2\n",
    "\n",
    "# 对角化\n",
    "eigenvalues_vmc = jnp.linalg.eigvalsh(E_matrix_sym)\n",
    "eigenvalues_vmc = jnp.sort(eigenvalues_vmc)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 60)\n",
    "print(\"NES-VMC 计算得到的激发态能量\")\n",
    "print(\"=\" * 60)\n",
    "for i, e in enumerate(eigenvalues_vmc):\n",
    "    exc = (e - eigenvalues_vmc[0]) * 27.2114\n",
    "    print(f\"E{i} = {e:.8f} Ha  |  激发能: {exc:.4f} eV\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 12. 与 FCI 结果对比"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 60)\n",
    "print(\"结果对比\")\n",
    "print(\"=\" * 60)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nVMC 结果:\")\n",
    "for i, e in enumerate(eigenvalues_vmc):\n",
    "    error = abs(e - E_fcis[i])\n",
    "    print(f\"E{i} = {e:.8f} Ha  |  误差: {error:.6f} Ha\")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nFCI 基准:\")\n",
    "for i, e in enumerate(E_fcis[:K]):\n",
    "    exc_eV = (e - E_fcis[0]) * 27.2114\n",
    "    print(f\"E{i} = {e:.8f} Ha  |  激发能: {exc_eV:.4f} eV\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 13. 总结\n",
    "\n",
    "本 notebook 实现了使用 NetKet 原生 API 风格的训练流程：\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **TotalAnsatz**：使用行列式形式的波函数\n",
    "2. **采样器**：使用 NetKet 的 MetropolisLocal 采样器\n",
